<p><strong>$25-50 Range:</strong> This sweet spot offers outstanding Christmas dinner wines. Seek Burgundian Pinot Noir from Côte Chalonnaise appellations like Mercurey, or Northern Rhône Crozes-Hermitage from producers like M. Chapoutier. These wines provide authentic terroir expression with food-pairing versatility.</p>

